===荣誉学院===
荣誉学院的设立宗旨是为成绩优异的学生提供额外的进修和实习机会以及一些福利待遇，从而达到鼓励所有在校生努力学习的目的。<ref name="Honors College">{{cite web|url=http://www.etsu.edu/honors/|title=Honors College|work=ETSU.edu|accessdate=2017-08-06|archive-date=2020-11-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201115192809/https://www.etsu.edu/honors/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

